00:17:08.041 --> 00:17:10.290
MICHAEL FRANTI: You use the
stuff that you don't want, and

00:17:10.290 --> 00:17:12.310
then they turn it into
something else?

00:17:12.310 --> 00:17:14.490
That's awesome, man.

00:17:14.490 --> 00:17:17.839
That's so cool.

00:17:17.839 --> 00:17:19.000
Anybody else?

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:21.453
You in the back there.

