00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:39.980
MICHAEL FRANTI: You break the
glass into little pieces and

00:17:39.980 --> 00:17:40.900
make it into something else.

00:17:40.900 --> 00:17:41.930
I love that.

00:17:41.930 --> 00:17:43.480
That was fun.

00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:45.204
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:17:45.204 --> 00:17:46.500
MICHAEL FRANTI: All right.

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:48.010
Nice.

00:17:48.010 --> 00:17:49.260
Any other kids?

00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:56.120
Do you compost?

